emote / emote                 Sends an emote to a chat contact

   Format:
      ;emote <name> <text>    Sends the emote <text> to the contact <name>

   Notes:
      The Chat task is used to chat with other players directly via telnet.
         Calls can be placed (or accepted) with any user whose MUD client uses
         the zChat or MudMaster protocols.
      This command is the equivalent of typing ';emote <text>' in every Chat
         task window that's connected to someone called <name>.

   User commands:
      emote
